And on the other hand, she thought,maybe there was still something 
there.  She smiled a little as they made thier way though the forest.
The rat on the other hand wasn't happy about someone taking up his 
soulder space.  He crawled up onto Scorponok's shoulder and rested 
there.  She smiled at seeing her pet get cozy on Scorponok's 
shoulder. She chuckled, "I think he likes you."
